    <refsection id="Description_mdaq_rc_controller">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
		
		This block decodes signals from RC controller. It can be used to create control system for drone or other devices 
		controlled with RC controller. Block supports channel controller and converts signals to values in 0-1000 range.
		
		</para>
    </refsection>
	
	<refsection id="InputOutput_mdaq_rc_controller">
        <title>Block Input/Output ports</title>
		<para>
		
		<member><para>output(1) - channel 1</para></member>
		<member><para>output(2) - channel 2</para></member>
		<member><para>output(3) - channel 3</para></member>
		<member><para>output(4) - channel 4</para></member>
		
		</para>
    
